extends baseEmail

block content
  h1 Email Verification
  p Hi #{firstName},
  
  p Welcome to our platform! Before you can start using your account, you need to verify your email address to ensure that we have the correct contact information. Please click the button below to verify your email:

  table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
    tbody
      tr
        td(align='center')
          table(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='10', cellspacing='0')
            tbody
              tr
                td.bg-blue(style='background-color: #3498db; border-radius: 5px;')
                  a(href=`${url}`, target='_blank', style='font-size: 16px; font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 15px 25px; border-radius: 2px; border: 1px solid #3498db; display: inline-block;') Verify Email

  p(style='margin-top: 20px;')
    | This verification link will expire in 24 hours. If the link expires, you can request a new verification link from user setting page.

  p(style='margin-top: 20px; color: #999;')
    | If you did not create an account using this email address, please ignore this email.

  p(style='margin-top: 20px;')
    | Thanks,
    br
    | The Team at Your Company
